{"tid":2416871,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"連加特：帶伊巴精神到韋斯咸","createTime":"2021-02-21T11:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T04:26:40.000Z","uid":31314,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dad55fcd20e36e7da2d99ccd4aa170f5b169fcd4","tid":2416871,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T11:50:21.000Z","msg":"英超韋斯咸中場連加特放話，將把伊巴謙莫域的爭勝精神帶給新隊友。英格蘭中場連加特（Jesse Lingard）1月由曼聯外借韋斯咸，表現翻生，首戰就梅開二度，上輪亦博到12碼，率領韋斯咸衝擊歐聯席位。<br />\n<br />\n「<strong><span class=\"red\">伊巴謙莫域來到曼聯時，他的求勝心就是完美的示範</span></strong>，當然摩連奴亦不相伯仲。」連加特接受《BT Sport》訪問時表示：「<strong><span class=\"red\">我和華舒福都在他們身上學到一二，希望自己能夠把經驗帶來韋斯咸。</span></strong>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「我知道勝利的感覺是如何，你必須專注，腦海中要維持每場波都要贏的信念。」連加特曾在2016年至2018年與伊巴和摩佬共事，贏得聯賽盃和歐霸盃錦標。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.manutd.com/AssetPicker/images/0/0/10/188/703519/ZLATAN_IBRAHIMOVIC_ALL_28_UNITED_GOALS-11586349347634_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.manutd.com%2FAssetPicker%2Fimages%2F0%2F0%2F10%2F188%2F703519%2FZLATAN_IBRAHIMOVIC_ALL_28_UNITED_GOALS-11586349347634_large.jpg&h=8d81608c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.thepeoplesperson.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/04075941/jesse-lingard-west-ham-debut-min.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.thepeoplesperson.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F04075941%2Fjesse-lingard-west-ham-debut-min.jpg&h=88a22745&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65c0a1b69f39decd63d1f4f5394eebac504ca1ab","tid":2416871,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f35458608a60d2e122bf5d4a0e9586ca181ffb3a","tid":2416871,"uid":200083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:17:20.000Z","msg":"真。球王"},{"pid":"5e652ce05c832260306c97087571f6825cfa40a2","tid":2416871,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:25:36.000Z","msg":"球皇連加特，唔係流料"},{"pid":"afee6364f5e77ddd3cc7d8b679be85ea30d78457","tid":2416871,"uid":372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dad55fcd20e36e7da2d99ccd4aa170f5b169fcd4","tid":2416871,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T11:50:21.000Z","msg":"英超韋斯咸中場連加特放話，將把伊巴謙莫域的爭勝精神帶給新隊友。英格蘭中場連加特（Jesse Lingard）1月由曼聯外借韋斯咸，表現翻生，首戰就梅開二度，上輪亦博到12碼，率領韋斯咸衝擊歐聯席位。<br />\n<br />\n「<strong><span class=\"red\">伊巴謙莫域來到曼聯時，他的求勝心就是完美的示範</span></strong>，當然摩連奴亦不相伯仲。」連加特接受《BT Sport》訪問時表示：「<strong><span class=\"red\">我和華舒福都在他們身上學到一二，希望自己能夠把經驗帶來韋斯咸。</span></strong>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「我知道勝利的感覺是如何，你必須專注，腦海中要維持每場波都要贏的信念。」連加特曾在2016年至2018年與伊巴和摩佬共事，贏得聯賽盃和歐霸盃錦標。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.manutd.com/AssetPicker/images/0/0/10/188/703519/ZLATAN_IBRAHIMOVIC_ALL_28_UNITED_GOALS-11586349347634_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.manutd.com%2FAssetPicker%2Fimages%2F0%2F0%2F10%2F188%2F703519%2FZLATAN_IBRAHIMOVIC_ALL_28_UNITED_GOALS-11586349347634_large.jpg&h=8d81608c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.thepeoplesperson.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/04075941/jesse-lingard-west-ham-debut-min.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.thepeoplesperson.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F04075941%2Fjesse-lingard-west-ham-debut-min.jpg&h=88a22745&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T08:47:11.000Z","msg":"自己官宣轉會算唔算伊巴